OL,3,CDriver charged after roof torn off bus
OL,4,Cin crash
OL,6,FA huge emergency service response
OL,7,Foccurred following the crash on Barton
OL,8,FRoad.
OL,10,FAn air ambulance was called, and
OL,11,Fmultiple paramedics attended the
OL,12,Fincident.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for Greater Manchester
OL,15,FPolice said: "Christopher Henry, of
OL,16,FThornhill Road, Tameside has been
OL,17,Fcharged with three counts of causing
OL,18,Fserious injury by dangerous driving.
OL,19,FHe has been bailed to attend
OL,20,FManchester Magistrates Court on
OL,21,FTuesday 15 September 2026.
