OL,3,CDriver charged after roof torn off bus
OL,4,Cin crash
OL,6,F"These charges come after a road
OL,7,Ftraffic collision involving a bus
OL,8,Fstriking a bridge which occurred on
OL,9,FMonday 21 July 2025 on Barton Road,
OL,10,FEccles."
